    "longBusinessSummary": "Ba Ria - Vung Tau House Development Joint Stock Company, together with its subsidiaries, engages in real estate business in Vietnam. It is involved in the development and construction of the urban area, housing, and industrial zone; implementing civil, industrial, and traffic engineering; real estate exchange management; and real estate brokerage and valuation activities. The company also trades in construction materials, houses, and real estate; and produces concrete and other cement related products. In addition, it engages in construction investment, post, tourism, and elevators repairing and maintaining activities; leasing concrete bumping machines and trucks; trucking activities; land use rights business; buying, selling, and leasing of houses; investing in refinery and infrastructure projects; organizing and executing inbound and outbound traveling trips; provision of transferring and hotel booking services; and construction and management of apartment and water parks. The company was founded in 1990 and is based in Vung Tau, Vietnam.",
